sequenceDiagram
    participant vLLM as vLLM Inference Servers
    participant Prom as Prometheus / Thanos Querier<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Collector as Metrics Collector
    participant SatEngine as Saturation Engine<br/>(60s interval)
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>(in-memory)
    participant VAReconciler as VA Reconciler
    participant Actuator as Actuator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA

    Note over SatEngine: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Loop

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Prom->>vLLM: Scrape vLLM metrics<br/>(KV cache, queue depth, tokens)
        SatEngine->>Prom: PromQL query (batch all VAs)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA token)
        Prom-->>SatEngine: Metric results<br/>(kv_cache_usage_perc, num_requests_waiting, etc.)
        SatEngine->>SatEngine: Run saturation analysis<br/>(V1 threshold / V2 token-level)
        SatEngine->>Cache: Publish scaling decisions
        Cache->>VAReconciler: Trigger via DecisionTrigger Channel
        VAReconciler->>K8sAPI: GET scale target replicas<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>VAReconciler: Current replicas
        VAReconciler->>K8sAPI: PATCH VA status (desired replicas)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        VAReconciler->>Actuator: Emit scaling metrics
        Actuator->>Actuator: Publish to local Prometheus registry<br/>(wva_desired_replicas, wva_desired_ratio)
    end

    Note over Prom,HPA: HPA/KEDA Scaling Execution

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Prom->>Actuator: Scrape /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Actuator-->>Prom: WVA custom metrics
        HPA->>Prom: Query wva_desired_replicas<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Prom-->>HPA: Desired replica count
        HPA->>K8sAPI: Scale Deployment/StatefulSet/LWS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end

    Note over Collector: Flow 2: EPP Metrics Scraping

    participant EPP as EPP Pods<br/>(Endpoint Picker)

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        VAReconciler->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool CRs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>VAReconciler: InferencePool events
        Collector->>EPP: Scrape flow control metrics<br/>HTTPS, Auth: Bearer Token (epp-metrics-token)
        EPP-->>Collector: queue_size, queue_bytes
        Collector->>SatEngine: Provide via source registry
    end

    Note over VAReconciler: Flow 3: ConfigMap Configuration Updates

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        VAReconciler->>K8sAPI: Watch ConfigMaps<br/>(saturation, scale-to-zero, queueing)
        K8sAPI-->>VAReconciler: ConfigMap change event
        VAReconciler->>VAReconciler: Update Unified Config
        VAReconciler->>SatEngine: Config refresh
    end
